A Tapestry 5 component that allows embedding a Vaadin Application inside a Tapestry page.

To use the component in a Tapestry page:

<html xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_1_0.xsd"
  xmlns:v="tapestry-library:tapestryvaadin">

  ...

  <v:embed url="http://url/of/your/vaadin/app"/>

  ...
</html>